%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F080416_baa45433f23fc8848eb86f5de3c3e98e.jpg&h=9aa58c1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180617/20423163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180617%2F20423163&d=wlsr4Qli7HxnravKwskRtS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=72e732e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180617%2F20423163&h=e81618a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180617/20423163</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T00:10:21.000Z","msg":"關我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T00:18:00.000Z","msg":"沙拿反諷拉莫斯打針論：他的說法很有趣<br />\n<br />\n沙拿於歐聯決賽提早因傷退下火線，皇家馬德里中堅沙治奧拉莫斯強調自己非故意令對方受傷，更指對方理應可以「紮住踢」。對於拉莫斯的言論，沙拿明顯不滿，更指對方言論使他哭笑不得。<br />\n沙拿：歐聯傷出係我生涯最差時刻<br />\n<br />\n拉莫斯早前指沙拿於歐聯決賽受傷後，只要接受注射治療便可「紮住踢」，以繼續為利物浦作賽。對於該皇馬中堅的言論，沙拿反擊道：「一個人先讓你哭，然後又逗你笑，他真的很好。或者他也知道我到底能否如期復出踢世界盃吧。他事後曾給我傳短訊，但我從沒對此說OK。」<br />\n<br />\n沙拿早前表明於歐聯決賽傷出，是他職業生涯中最艱難的時候，不過他亦明言自己對於世界盃復出信心十足。（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=wlsr4Qli7HxnravKwskRtS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f653064c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"9abedc08d5202ccb2a6ff0f120d986bfe9183743","tid":710531,"uid":44396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T00:20:16.000Z","msg":"怨撚夠未死痢狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a1bf73ada4a810686026922e65bc5811a58aa9","tid":710531,"uid":27485,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T00:30:50.000Z","msg":"何輝第一場講埃及個陣大概講過<br />\n一隊有實力既球隊<br />\n係唔應該因為一兩個球員缺陣<br />\n而搞到唔識踢波<br />\n依家埃及就證明到<br />\n冇左沙拿一樣可以踢番佢地既足球<br />\n<br />\n其實講得好岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然最後都係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b54075ef986d3c86a4863ed47614073c4a3b26b","tid":710531,"uid":22589,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T00:57:31.000Z","msg":"牙朗帶住垃圾隊友都偷到一場<br />\n沙拿咁撚勁 上場屌打左俄羅斯未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133aededca1f71ce1ca7d9137ec94559525ee89a","tid":710531,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:09:27.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n使唔使鋪埋紅地毯等沙拿場場入波呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81a5f62dd2b6a755ea57610be0a4c1754b7e5fa","tid":710531,"uid":32733,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35f3d384052242fef56bca73f62f89075cce19e8","tid":710531,"uid":15647,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7c415590bae9412e0a2530a3574a4ee58e89d1bf","tid":710531,"uid":32733,"like":9,"dislike":11,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T23:56:49.000Z","msg":"自從果場之後好想拉莫斯被人收山就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：完全唔覺得拉莫斯係冇心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T23:58:43.000Z","msg":"係呀係呀，一定係沙拿唔小心撓住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T02:55:37.000Z","msg":"我唔係講冇左沙拿搞到輸乜乜物物, 我都唔撚係利迷, 我只係覺得拉莫斯好撚仆街, 而佢都唔係第一次, 佢唔撚係粗暴防守一野屌落你度果D, 而係陰濕, 做埋D有機會整到人受傷既小動作, 當然我唔會知佢腦入面諗咩, 冇人知, 但係睇左拉莫斯踢咁耐波, 係咪特登都心裡有數"}]}